{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Together with Souryuu\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2: Instruct Me, Souryuu!<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I heard that Souryuu's hobby was playing hanafuda, so I decided to learn it as a way of finding some common ground with her.","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Sakura Dorms","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_room","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... Today, we'll be going over the Battle of Okehazama.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Hmm... At last, the great battle that led to the country's unification!","dir":1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301590},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"At that time, the Imagawa clan had a numbers advantage... Oh my, Commander. What brings you here?","dir":1,"side":1,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Ask what she is doing."}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Isn't it obvious? It's a history lesson!","actor":301590,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Indeed. Urakaze wants to deepen her understanding of the Sengoku period, so I'm giving her a lesson.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Commander, you're welcome to join if you're interested.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I suppose it wouldn't hurt to listen.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030,"bgName":"bg_story_room","withoutActorName":true},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... Nobody could have foreseen that Imagawa Yoshimoto would be slain by Nobunaga's attack.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"In the aftermath of the battle, the Oda clan...","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... All right, that concludes today's lesson.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Amazing... Souryuu's lesson was informative, but also very easy to follow.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hm, hm... I see! Thank you very much, teacher!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301590},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Teach us something else next!","actor":301590,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Of course. It would be my pleasure.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Something else...? I was beginning to think that Souryuu knew everything...","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Commander, your thoughts are written all over your face... This is simply part of a secretary's duties.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Now, did you need something?","dir":1,"side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"\"Could you teach me hanafuda?\""}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"You want to learn hanafuda? Why the sudden interest...?","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"However, if you are genuinely interested in learning, I wouldn't mind teaching you...","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"And thus, I began to learn hanafuda from Souryuu.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"CANGLONG2","fadeOut":1.5}